Maxima.. near the edge of the cliff, heard the communique. But.. unable to 
obey her orders. 

She herself was a wreck. The damage too great to move.

Her optics watched as the Predacons retreated. Her optics watched Hydras. 
But, she feared saying anything ... aloud. Softly, a whisper escaped... 
"Hydras," as she laid there ready to black out once more. 

Her audio receptors could hear the last bits of battle as it ended. & not far 
from her, she heard Rodimus. 

She laid there... & listened. Contemplating. Wondering if she would cease to 
exist out here or not. 


--part1_1aa.129d3ef3.2bc25044_boundary
